componentDescription: An unstyled select item to be used within a Select.

closeOnClick.description: If true, the select will close when the select option is clicked.

disabled.description: If true, the select option will be disabled.

id.description: The id of the select option.

label.description: A text representation of the select option's content. Used for keyboard text navigation matching.

onClick.description: The click handler for the select option.

value.description: The value of the select option.
